Use the standard library
This is how to pluck of arr:
   Remember that n is arr's length
   When n is 0, then:
      The answer is []
   End when
   Remember that best is item 0 in arr
   Remember that besti is 0
   Remember that i is 1
   Do this diff of n and 1 times:
      Remember that x is item i in arr
      When x is less than best, then:
         Remember that best is x
         Remember that besti is i
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is [best, besti]
Now you know